      "locked": false,
      "text": "nums_set = set(nums)              => O(n)\nfor i in range(1, n + 1):         => O(n) \n    if i not in nums_set:         => O(1)\n\n\nresult.append(i)                  => O(1)\n\n\n\n        O(n) + O(n) = O(n)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "nums_set = set(nums)              => O(n)\nfor i in range(1, n + 1):         => O(n) \n    if i not in nums_set:         => O(1)\n\n\nresult.append(i)                  => O(1)\n\n\n\n        O(n) + O(n) = O(n)"
    },
